    <item>
      <title>阿达尼和丰益国际将于下月开始出售合资企业股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/adani-wilmar-are-said-to-start-stake-sale-in-venture-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，阿达尼企业有限公司 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 和丰益国际有限公司 (Wilmar International Ltd.) 预计将最早于下个月开始出售其消费合资企业阿达尼丰益国际有限公司 (Adani Wilmar Ltd.) 的少数股权，以遵守股权规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/adani-wilmar-are-said-to-start-stake-sale-in-venture-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 09:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
